              <span id="reviewTextContainer1361419596" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7907740401912421239">Mahbod Seraji has created a coming of age story that appeals to all ages.Set against the Iranian Revolution in the 1970&apos;s, the story twists and turns through complex plot moves in a well structured story. Pasha, Ahmed, Zari, Faheemah, Doctor, and The Masked Angel are the main characters who the reader learns to love and cannot resist discovering their destinies.</span>
  <span id="freeText7907740401912421239" style="display:none">Mahbod Seraji has created a coming of age story that appeals to all ages.Set against the Iranian Revolution in the 1970's, the story twists and turns through complex plot moves in a well structured story. Pasha, Ahmed, Zari, Faheemah, Doctor, and The Masked Angel are the main characters who the reader learns to love and cannot resist discovering their destinies.</span>
